{
  "texts": [
    "ChatGPT can be integrated with workflow automation tools to streamline processes and reduce errors.",
    "For example, ChatGPT can be used to automate approval workflows, where employees can ask ChatGPT to initiate the approval process and track the progress of their request.",
    "(Amber & Hashmi, 2023; Dwivedi et al., 2023; Englund & Jayne, 2023; Narendra et al., 2017) I n d u s t r i a l M a n a g e m e n t & D a t a S y s t e m s 5.",
    "Analytics and reporting: ChatGPT can be used to capture data on employee interactions and provide insights into knowledge usage, knowledge gaps, and training needs.",
    "This data can be used to improve the knowledge base and training materials and to inform decisions about future investments in knowledge management."
  ]
}